145
00:09:41,830 --> 00:09:43,310
Sekarang bahkan Jiufeng pun
tidak kelihatan.

146
00:09:44,110 --> 00:09:45,990
(Fu Chengjin ini kejam sekali.)

147
00:09:46,260 --> 00:09:48,190
(Dia bahkan tidak mengantarku
di perjalanan terakhirku.)

148
00:09:48,218 --> 00:09:51,120
(Aula Hanyuan)

149
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:03,020
