163
00:10:45,140 --> 00:10:46,230
Bilian sudah meninggal.

164
00:10:46,590 --> 00:10:49,260
Jika diberi waktu lagi,
dan Pangeran Jin juga celaka, bagaimana?

165
00:10:51,500 --> 00:10:52,070
Aliya,

166
00:10:53,780 --> 00:10:55,950
apakah kau tahu kau telah melakukan
kejahatan menipu Kaisar?

167
00:10:59,260 --> 00:10:59,710
Ayah,

168
00:11:00,620 --> 00:11:02,110
