176
00:11:20,380 --> 00:11:21,990
Namun, jika kaki Pangeran Jin
tidak sembuh,

177
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:24,140
artinya itu kejahatan menipu Kaisar.

178
00:11:24,990 --> 00:11:27,380
