224
00:14:35,070 --> 00:14:36,350
Bagus.

225
00:14:37,830 --> 00:14:38,230
Ayah.

226
00:14:46,860 --> 00:14:47,470
Semua ini

227
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:49,860
